def suite(card)
  card[1]
end
def rank(card)
  case card[0]
    when "2".."9"
      return card[0].to_i
    when "T"
      return 10
    when "J"
      return 11
    when "Q"
      return 12
    when "K"
      return 13
    when "A"
      return 14
  end
end
def less(card1, card2, lead, trump)
  cost1 = rank(card1)
  cost1 += 13 if suite(card1) == lead
  cost1 += 26 if suite(card1) == trump
  cost2 = rank(card2)
  cost2 += 13 if suite(card2) == lead
  cost2 += 26 if suite(card2) == trump
  cost1 < cost2
end
